channel.title: Help needed (have no name for the error)
channel.description:
Well, I have this classic error many get these days... I can login to my server using my portforwarded ip. I have correctly opened the port on my router and enabled it on my firewall. But of course... no1 else can login.
Actually, it worked fine until I started on a new project, so I bet it's server-sided. If it's not, lock or move it if you must.
I do not see a reason for pics, as I know I portforwarded it right, as I no how 2 PF. But, if you need a pic, tell me what you need a pic of, and I'll try to get it.
